data.description: Discover serene lake living on Star Lake in Otter Tail County. This remarkable property spans 2.14 acres, offering an idyllic retreat for fishing enthusiasts and recreation lovers. With 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, the open and inviting house provides ample space for gatherings. Bask in natural light, enjoy the walkout basement with captivating lakefront views, and make use of the 134 feet of private lake shore for swimming, boating, and fishing. The 2-stall attached garage and detached storage building cater to convenience. Embrace tranquility, seclusion, and picturesque views. Own a piece of paradise call your favorite Realtor for a showing!
